ISLAMABAD, Nov 08 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb Tuesday said Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif had addressed the COP27 high-level segment of Saudi Green Initiative and highlighted salient features of Green Pakistan Project which championed journey towards green future.
She, in a tweet, said the prime minister also underscored urgency to curb escalating pollution by utilizing modern technology.
